original_title: The Aquabats! Kooky Spooky Halloween Party
overview: Coming straight to you from a secret bunker in Southern California, The Aquabats have put together a fully-produced show so that we can all get together for Halloween, celebrate the release of "Kooky Spooky... in Stereo!" and make up for all the live touring we DIDN'T get to do this year! It's a concert and a party... all in one!!
title: The Aquabats! Kooky Spooky Halloween Party
